assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Jinmao Property Services Co., Limited, an investment holding company, provides property management services in the People's Republic of China. It offers property management services for property owners and residents, and property developers; security, cleaning, greening, gardening, and repair and maintenance services for the operation of common area facilities; and residential communities, commercial, and office properties primarily comprising office buildings and shopping malls, as well as public properties, including schools, government facilities, and other public spaces. The company also provides value-added services for non-property owners consist of sales assistance services to property developers, and consultancy and other value-added services; and community value-added services for property owners and residents of its managed properties to address their daily lifestyle needs, which consist of platform services for interior decoration, community living services, community space operation services, and real estate brokerage services. In addition, it offers technology development and services; and real estate brokerage, city operation, and smart community management services. The company was formerly known as Jinmao Property Development Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Jinmao Property Services Co., Limited in October 2021. Jinmao Property Services Co., Limited was founded in 1993 and is based in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Jinmao Property Services Co., Limited is a subsidiary of China Jinmao Holdings Group Limited.
